Creat a 2d 9x7 array named board which show the original of the game

for loop{

Prompt gamer 1 to choose the column they want to place their tokens
If the gamer 1 type invalid input
Let the gamer 1 to input again

Change the element " " into X at the column that gamer 1 input

Call fuction checkWinner
Check each element in the array
If board[i][j] != 0 && board[i][j]==board[i][j+1] && board[i][j]==board[i][j+2] && board[i][j]==board[i][j+3] 
Then return 1
 else return 0

When get the return
If return=0
Prompt gamer 2 to choose the column they want to place their tokens
If the gamer 2 type invalid input
Let the gamer 2 to input again

Change the element " " into O at the column that gamer 2 input

Call fuction checkWinner
Check each element in the array
If board[i][j] != 0 && board[i][j]==board[i][j+1] && board[i][j]==board[i][j+2] && board[i][j]==board[i][j+3] 
